                     <interp inst="t18130407-35-off198" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bigamy"></interp>
               that he, on the 10th of December, 1809, at the Parish Church of St. George, Hanover-square, took to wife one 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130407-35-victim367" type="victimName">
                           Elizabeth 
                           Life
                        <interp inst="t18130407-35-victim367" type="surname" value="Life"></interp>
