                  , that he afterwards, at the parish church of St. Andrew, Holborn, took to wife one 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130407-35-victim369" type="victimName">
                           Sarah Catherine 
                           Bailey
                        <interp inst="t18130407-35-victim369" type="surname" value="Bailey"></interp>
